        <h2 align="center">Learn about your Feline Heritage</h2>

			<h2 align="center">What is a cat?</h2>

			
			<p>Binomial name (scientific name):<b><i> Felis Catus</i></b></p>
			<p>In Latin, <b><em>bi</em></b> means two or both, and <b><em>nomen</b></em> means name.  All animals have a scientific Latin name with two parts to it.</p>

			<p>Sometimes cats are also called felines and this comes from its Latin name <b><em>felis</b></em>.</b></p>
					
